// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Task - AM_VigToVil_SL6-7_Task_01 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Dialog - Abigor 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Page Intro Text :
"P961861105" "Kel'Morgath imprisoned me with a clever magical trick. Rest assured that shall not happen again. But I am still bound to the contract forged between us. I taught him how to construct the Foci of Binding, an artifact of power that links the power of two souls together into one, and the expense of the weaker of the two. In exchange for this knowledge, Kel'Morgath offered me his soul, but I did not know then that his soul was one of the Circle, for their souls are already owed to me and mine."
// Answer Text :
"P1320859365" "Why does he want the Foci of Binding?"
// Page InformationPage1 Text :
"P667729189" "To increase his power, of course. He has a noble plan to use the Foci to gain enough power in order to fulfill the ancient agreement between the people of Oranbega and my demon overlords. Should he succeed then his soul would still be mine, but his people would be saved. The agreement, however, requires that the bloodline of Mu should be forever extinguished, their souls offered up to us in repayment for our service to them in your distant past.<br><br>With the foci draining power from his prisoner he is strong now, strong enough to keep me enslaved, too strong for you."
// Answer Text :
"P323258221" "Where can I find this prisoner?"
// Page InformationPage2 Text :
"P2092960021" "The prisoner is here, in Kel'Morgath's sanctum, guarded by the succubus, Raveshna. His power is almost gone, and soon his soul will be mine, but Kel'Morgath has already chosen the man's daughter as his next victim, and she is even more powerful than her father."
// Answer Text :
"P2210095319" "How can I stop Kel'Morgath?"
// Page InformationPage3 Text :
"P1275660427" "It is simple. Without a victim to drain power from, Kel'Morgath will weaken. Use the Foci of Binding, drain all the power from his prisoner and use it against Kel'Morgath. Once defeated his soul is mine for the taking! But first, you must use the Foci to release me from my enslavement."
// Answer Text :
"P1577232536" "How do I know you won't turn on me?"
// Page InformationPage4 Text :
"P737734881" "I am still bound by my contract with Kel'Morgath, so I can do no direct harm to him. You are the only one who can defeat him and deliver his soul to me. But in order for me to claim his soul, I must be free of his magic. If you defeat him without freeing me, he will return another day to begin his plot anew.<br><br>This is the only way."
// Answer Text :
"P4073527449" "Very well, demon. I release you!"
// Page InformationPage5 Text :
"P3187550215" "<color orange>The demon vanishes before your eyes, pulled back into the hellish realm from whence in came.</color>"
// Answer Text :
"P455845946" ""Find the prisoner" (Leave)"

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Dialog - Hostage 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Page Intro Text :
"P3970473963" "A... A hero... From Paragon City.<br><br>I never thought I would be happy to see one of you. I... I am very weak. The wizard is using an artifact to drain my power in order to feed his own. He... He has said my daughter is next. Please, I must escape, my presence is only feeding him more power. He will destroy you!"
// Answer Text :
"P909317550" "No running, we need to stop Kel'Morgath now."
// Page InformationPage1 Text :
"P1897512416" "I am of no use to you, my power is drained. How do you plan to oppose him? He is too powerful!<br><br>Augh... I... I can feel demons clawing at my soul. If I do not escape soon then they will claim it. I must get to the Midnight Squad. They will be able to keep me safe, at least long enough to see my daughter again, safe and out of danger of this madman."
// Answer Text :
"P418284519" "Where is Kel'Morgath?"
// Page InformationPage2 Text :
"P1190784133" "He's here, no doubt planning the abduction of my daughter. We must rescue my daughter and get to the Midnighters; perhaps together we can gather our strength and oppose him."
// Answer Text :
"P294153810" "There is no time, the time to strike Kel'Morgath is now!"
// Page InformationPage3 Text :
"P1795040631" "You are blinded by vengeance. Removing me from Kel'Morgath's grasp will already strike a blow against him. It is far wiser to rally our strength after putting him off balance and then to strike the decisive blow. Kel'Morgath must die, that much I agree with, but striking now will lead to my death, of that I am certain."
// Answer Text :
"P1873175185" "Fight Kel'Morgath and you may die, fight me and I guarantee it."

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Task Header Items 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// IntroString :
"P2730213379" "Your investigation of the strange magical trinket suggests that it transmits the inherent magical energy from one individual to another. Kel'Morgath is using these types of artifacts to steal the power of others, that's why he is so powerful! If he were to get his hands on someone truly powerful, who knows how destructive that could be. There is no choice left, Kel'Morgath must be stopped no matter the cost!"
// AcceptString :
"P628425909" "Stop Kel'Morgath"
// SendOffString :
"P3597491878" "Kel'Morgath's lair is located within the labyrinthine depths of Oranbega, the city of the Circle of Thorns. The trinket you discovered should enable you to navigate its depths and infiltrate into Kel'Morgath's inner sanctum. Once inside your only chance to defeat Kel'Morgath is to use the power of his trinket against him."
// ActiveTaskString :
"P2963670230" "Eliminate Kel'Morgath's Source of Power"
// YoureStillBusyString :
"P393698290" "Who knows how many of these trinkets Kel'Morgath has and how many victims he is draining to empower himself. You must strike against Kel'Morgath now, or there may not be another chance."
// TaskTitle :
"P2180826002" "<font face=title><scale 1.1><span align=center><color orange>A Strange Mystical Trinket</color></span></scale></font><br><span align=center><color slategray><i>Villain Mission</i></color></span>"

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// MissionDef 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// EntryString :
"P1378731285" "As you enter Kel'Morgath's lair you discard your disguise as one of the Circle of Thorns. The time for deceit is over, now is the time for action!"
// ExitStringSuccess :
"P671172543" "<font face=title><scale 1.1><span align=center><color orange>A Strange Mystic Trinket</color></span></scale></font><br><span align=center><color slategray><i>Alignment Mission</i></color></span><br><br>The sinister wizard, Kel'Morgath, has been defeated, but at the cost of Orsen Greenfield's life. Such sacrifices are of no concern to you, Orsen was an Arachnos Mystic. That his death also doomed Kel'Morgath is probably the greatest contribution he ever offered to the rest of humanity."
// Script Variable BOSS_DISPLAYNAME :
"P3383608100" "Nothing"
// Script Variable BOSS_DISPLAYINFO :
"P856364347" ""

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Objective - ScriptTalkedToDemon 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Description :
"P1658830099" "Learn about Kel'Morgath's trinket"
// Script Variable BOSS_DISPLAYNAME :
"P3221251797" "Abigor"
// Script Variable BOSS_INACTIVE_DIALOG :
"P3893207120" "<shout>Gloat now, children of Ermeeth, but your souls are still owed to me and mine! This imprisonment shall end, and when it does, I shall devour your souls one by one!"
// Script Variable BOSS_ATTACK_DIALOG :
"P520749034" "You! You carry the Foci of Binding! You can destroy Kel'Morgath and set me free. In return I shall devour his eternal soul!"
// Script Variable SaysList :
"P4112170332" "Move quickly, mortal, Kel'Morgath will soon discover that I am gone."
// Script Variable SaysList :
"P1738482053" "Nevermind"
// Script Variable HOSTAGE_NAME :
"P2214766382" "Orsen Greenfield"
// Script Variable HOSTAGE_INACTIVE_DIALOG :
"P4136188108" "<shout>Aaaauuuugh!"
// Script Variable HOSTAGE_ACTIVE_DIALOG :
"P2805958814" "Help me! Please!"
// Script Variable SayOnRescue :
"P2950891055" "We must flee. The wizard... He will steal your power!"
// Script Variable CAPTOR_NAME :
"P2489954669" "Raveshna"
// Script Variable CAPTOR_INACTIVE_DIALOG :
"P2852993871" "Once the master has drained your magic, your soul is mine, little man."
// Script Variable CAPTOR_ACTIVE_DIALOG :
"P1456692209" "What? Only one possessing the Foci of Binding could intrude here! My master will reward me well for delivering you to him!"
// Script Variable BOSS_DISPLAYNAME :
"P3019987874" "Nerva Spectra Daemon"
// Script Variable StatusString :
"P495031116" "Bring Orsen to Kel'Morgath"
// Script Variable WaveShout :
"P1907264824" "<shout>Destroy the intruder!"
// Script Variable Greeting :
"P1875711363" "Th... Thank you."
// Script Variable SaysList :
"P1006253633" "Auugh... No... He's draining my magic!"
// Script Variable SaysList :
"P455043761" "Please, {HeroName}. If he draws away more of my power then my soul will be forfeit!"
// Script Variable SaysList :
"P450333205" "You! You've damned me for all eternity! For that I curse you to the deepest, darkest pit of hell and wish the agony of a thousand hells upon you!<em>AAAAAAAAAAAAAGGGGH!"

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Objective - ScriptHostageRescued 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Description :
"P3047439444" "Find Raveshna and the prisoner"
// Script Variable BOSS_DISPLAYNAME :
"P2614593066" "Kel'Morgath"
// Script Variable BOSS_INACTIVE_DIALOG :
"P1299114754" "<shout>I sense a familiar magic... No! Another Foci of Binding. It is countering my wardings!"
// Script Variable BOSS_ATTACK_DIALOG :
"P3901078217" "{HeroName}, stop! If you continue your attack then both our souls will be destroyed forever!"
// Script Variable BOSS_1STBLOOD_DIALOG :
"P4211663866" "Are you so black hearted that you would resort to the same vile magic as I?"
// Script Variable BOSS_75HEALTH_DIALOG :
"P3136348248" "If you do not stop your assault then I will consume that man's soul and destroy both of our souls! His death will be on your shoulders!"
// Script Variable BOSS_50HEALTH_DIALOG :
"P2299128208" "Did you now hear me, {HeroName}? You are bargaining with that man's soul! I will destroy him if I have to!"
// Script Variable BOSS_25HEALTH_DIALOG :
"P3776661293" "I... I... I can't! I can't damn that man's soul to the same hell awaiting my people. If you drain him any further then both of our souls will be forfeit."
// Script Variable BOSS_DEAD_DIALOG :
"P4109208275" "Heh, your determination may have won you this battle, {HeroName}, but believe me when I tell you that you do not understand the cost you have just paid. The war for your very soul has only just begun!"
// Script Variable BOSS_KILLEDHERO_DIALOG :
"P1957484553" "You are dealing with power far beyond your feeble grasp, {HeroName}. Had you been more ruthless you might have prevailed!"
// Script Variable Greeting :
"P1127431811" "Hello, {HeroName}."

