"P653613332" "Kel'Morgath has been destroyed, but at what cost? He warned you that the battle was won, but that the war for your soul had only just begun. No matter. In the war between good and evil, there will always be casualties. If you are to be one of these casualties, then the need to make a difference is even greater!"

