"P2141217566" "I found this crazy trinket in the park yesterday. It's totally weird, I wonder where it came from."

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Task - AM_VigToVil_SL6-7_Task_02 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Dialog - TattooArtist 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Page Intro Text :
"P56160514" "Sky Dragon's ancestors are eagerly awaiting to fight at his side. Why is it that you are here, {HeroName}?"
// Answer Text :
"P4212954293" "How do the tattoos work?"
// Page InformationPage1 Text :
"P881656074" "The spiritual tattoos I create only work for those who are chosen by the spirits. The Ancestor Spirits must choose to answer the call to aid the recipient, as they have agreed to do with Sky Dragon. The ink I use to create the link between our two worlds requires the blood of the recipient in order to work. It is a great power to bestow upon Sky Dragon, one that I happily perform. I have trained all my life to perfect the art of linking the dead to the living. The spirits have assured me that there is a place of honor for me in heaven when my time comes. One day, my children's grand children will call upon my spirit to aid them in this world, and when the time is right aid them I shall."
// Answer Text :
"P1211813380" "I am worthy of being chosen."
// Page InformationPage2 Text :
"P1520633327" "No. No! You are not chosen, this power is not for you, it is for Sky Dragon and no other! Hear you not my words? The spirits have chosen him to bestow their power upon. It will not work for you."
// Answer Text :
"P3134824909" "Sky Dragon is unworthy, you will bestow this power unto me."
// Page InformationPage3 Text :
"P3362855260" "I will do no such thing! The power will not work for you. Now leave or I will force you to leave!"
// Answer Text :
"P4191038958" "Then it shall be destroyed!"

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Task Header Items 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// IntroString :
"P3874864550" "Sky Dragon means well, but his sense of honor is misguided at best. Tsoo tattoo magic is powerful. If it can be believed that they are going to waste it on Sky Dragon, then there is likely a hidden agenda at work here. Only you can be certain that the power wouldn't be wasted or used to do evil through you. You'll be doing Sky Dragon a favor."
// AcceptString :
"P1454463600" "Take the tattoo magic for yourself"
// SendOffString :
"P2251572104" "The Tsoo are untrustworthy, they must be planning to trick Sky Dragon with this promise of power, potentially even plotting to use the tattoo magic to control him! You need to stop Sky Dragon before he makes a big mistake, and then, if the power is real, take the tattoo magic unto yourself. Only you are worthy of such power!"
// YoureStillBusyString :
"P622141558" "Get to the Tattoo Artist's shop and stop Sky Dragon before it is too late. If the tattoo magic is real, then you must force the Tsoo Artist to bestow you with its mystical power. Nobody else can be trusted with such power."
// TaskTitle :
"P1025348104" "<font face=title><scale 1.1><span align=center><color orange>You Get Hit In The Face!</color></span></scale></font><br><span align=center><color slategray><i>Villain Mission</i></color></span>"

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// MissionDef 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// EntryString :
"P4067707267" "The stink of exotic incense confirms that this warehouse is the Tsoo hideout you have been looking for."
// ExitStringSuccess :
"P2388048762" "<font face=title><scale 1.1><span align=center><color orange>You Get Hit In The Face!</color></span></scale></font><br><span align=center><color slategray><i>Alignment Mission</i></color></span><br><br>You may not have been able to get the mystical power from the Tsoo's Tattoo magic, but at least Sky Dragon isn't running around with it either. That fool would have probably ended up working for the Tsoo if you hadn't realized how unlikely it would be for the Tsoo to gift someone like him with such power. Perhaps now Sky Dragon will see the error of his ways and realize, as you have, that only the strong can be entrusted with such power."
// Script Variable ObjectiveUIText :
"P1645546263" "Find the Tattoo Artist and talk with him"
// Script Variable BOSS_DISPLAYNAME :
"P2070558533" "Sky Dragon"
// Script Variable BOSS_INACTIVE_DIALOG :
"P2809696394" "I am unsure whether I should do this. It is a great gift of power, but the Tsoo are untrustworthy..."
// Script Variable BOSS_ATTACK_DIALOG :
"P2452918411" "{HeroName}? What are you doing here? No, I do not wish to fight you, but I will if you try to stop me from obtaining my ancestral power!"
// Script Variable BOSS_1STBLOOD_DIALOG :
"P1895753466" "{HeroName}! I am not working for the Tsoo, I am using them to grant me power that I can use for good, not evil!"
// Script Variable BOSS_75HEALTH_DIALOG :
"P856100967" "With this power that the Tsoo offer me I can do more to help the innocent than I ever could before."
// Script Variable BOSS_50HEALTH_DIALOG :
"P2904124939" "You have forced my hand, {HeroName}. Flee while you can.<shout>Blood Moon! Aid me!"
// Script Variable BOSS_25HEALTH_DIALOG :
"P4245988181" "I will never remove this stain on my honor, fighting you along side the evil Tsoo. Why have you forced me to do this, {HeroName}?"
// Script Variable BOSS_DEAD_DIALOG :
"P4003166108" "I see now... you knew that the power... would corrupt me... thank you for... returning me... to the true path..."
// Script Variable BOSS_KILLEDHERO_DIALOG :
"P2530288043" "You see, {HeroName}. Good intentions alone are not enough to vanquish your enemy. But have I become that which I seek to vanquish?"
// Script Variable SaysList :
"P2836457115" "Now you die!"

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Objective - ScriptSkyDragonDown 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Description :
"P3539515447" "Stop Sky Dragon"
// Script Variable BOSS_DISPLAYNAME :
"P2530715143" "Blood Moon"
// Script Variable BOSS_INACTIVE_DIALOG :
"P2770001921" "<shout>No harm shall come to Sky Dragon, the newest brother of the Hmong Tsoo!"
// Script Variable BOSS_ATTACK_DIALOG :
"P813392982" "I will strip the flesh from your bones for this insult, {HeroName}. Nobody attacks one of the Hmong Tsoo and lives!"
// Script Variable BOSS_1STBLOOD_DIALOG :
"P3591588012" "Pathetic!"
// Script Variable BOSS_50HEALTH_DIALOG :
"P1634792185" "Sky Dragon's ancestor spirits are strong. They will make the Hmong Tsoo strong as well."
// Script Variable BOSS_DEAD_DIALOG :
"P2168637931" "I curse you to the hell of being torn apart by a thousand demons, {HeroName}!"
// Script Variable BOSS_KILLEDHERO_DIALOG :
"P2791033385" "Only now, in defeat, do you see that my Crescent technique is invincible!"
// Script Variable SaysList :
"P3105238962" "Your fate is sealed, {HeroName}. This attack will not go unanswered!"

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Objective - ScriptBloodMoonDown 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Description :
"P3482926303" "Defeat Blood Moon"
// Script Variable BOSS_DISPLAYNAME :
"P264971279" "Tattoo Artist"
// Script Variable BOSS_DISPLAYINFO :
"P1108051688" "The dedicated tattoo artists of the Tsoo have little combat ability on their own, but their mastery of the Tsoo's tattoo magic allows them to imbue others in that organization with phenomenal powers."
// Script Variable BOSS_INACTIVE_DIALOG :
"P46480057" "The power of Sky Dragon's ancestors are waiting to join him in his fight."
// Script Variable BOSS_ATTACK_DIALOG :
"P3124683927" "I cannot allow you to destroy my work. It is dedicated to Sky Dragon and his ancestors, not to you, {HeroName}."
// Script Variable BOSS_1STBLOOD_DIALOG :
"P3985869524" "You... You struck me!"
// Script Variable BOSS_75HEALTH_DIALOG :
"P3410089153" "My Silkworm style will confound you!"
// Script Variable BOSS_50HEALTH_DIALOG :
"P687403103" "Painting Mantis style will destroy you!"
// Script Variable BOSS_25HEALTH_DIALOG :
"P990572054" "You are strong, but wicked of heart, {HeroName}. The spirits will curse your name!"
// Script Variable BOSS_DEAD_DIALOG :
"P4143987748" "You have performed a great insult to the spirits. I curse you with a thousand lifetimes of pain and suffering for what you have done!"
// Script Variable BOSS_KILLEDHERO_DIALOG :
"P4060563639" "Ah ha ha haaaa. The spirits have abandoned you, {HeroName}, for I am favored by them."
// Script Variable Greeting :
"P4087299209" "Where is Sky Dragon? Where is Blood Moon?"

