// Script Variable SaysList :
"P472799097" "<t=5 caption x= 0.2 y=0.2 d=4><scale 1.75><color white><bgcolor FireBrick>Transfer. Completed. Dispatch. ARES.<t=5 caption x= 0.2 y=0.4 d=4><scale 1.75><color white><bgcolor FireBrick>Neutralize. {HeroName}. Defend. MARS. Neutralize. {HeroName}. Defend. MARS."
