// Dialog :
"P4058384022" "You destroyed the military A.I. known as MARS and killed the insane inventor, Dr. Hargrove, who chose to defend his insane, mass murdering, super computer instead of let you destroy it. MARS was right though, humanity will always choose to destroy the sentient computer. Because we are afraid of that which we cannot control."

