"P3033909315" "Vandercreek Labs went out of business after the Freakshow ransacked their facility and destroyed their new top secret project."

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Task - AM_VigToVil_SL6-7_Task_04 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Dialog - AgentDialogue 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Page Intro Text :
"P362607671" "How... How did you learn about this meeting? Who sent you? Was it Requiem, was it Anton?"
// Answer Text :
"P1320296710" "Tell me what you know, Jonas Howe."
// Page AgentPlans Text :
"P2348961643" "I've been working within the 5th Column ever since the Reichsman returned. I've been gathering data for over a year. I suspected that my superiors were growing suspicious of my activities, so I decided to defect now rather than face my inevitable discovery."
// Answer Text :
"P647889374" "Tell me everything you told the Council"
// Page AgentIdentification Text :
"P2829649234" ""I helped them win several engagements in the past with some leaked intelligence, just enough to let them know I was legitimate, but I saved this data as insurance."<br><br><color orange>He hands you a small micro-disc.</color>"
// Answer Text :
"P2060040488" "What's on this disc?"
// Page AgentImportantInformation Text :
"P3680084912" "I'll tell you! Just don't kill me. This data holds the identities of every 5th Column agent within the Council's ranks, and every known Council agent that has infiltrated the 5th Column. With this information the Council will be able to feed their moles with false information, and ignore the false information fed to their own moles within the 5th Column. Victory will be assured for them!"
// Answer Text :
"P4143613022" "I see you know all about traitors and cowards. Now die like one."
// Page AgentDeath Text :
"P1302070361" "Wait! What? No!"
// Answer Text :
"P3988895464" "Hide the body and continue with your mission."

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Dialog - BossDialogue 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Page Intro Text :
"P496810247" "Nachtkrieg? How am I to know that you are trustworthy? The information you have provided in the past has proven... useful, so why defect? Perhaps you are counting on such a bold move to blind me to your true motives?"
// Answer Text :
"P4227345259" "I have information that you cannot afford to ignore or dismiss."
// Page InformationPage1 Text :
"P2569375210" "It is funny you say that. Information, which I chose not to ignore or dismiss, has come to my attention that the true Nachtkrieg's body has been hidden within a ventilation duct... So I ask you, who are you really?"
// Answer Text :
"P68937325" "Take down the Commander"

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Dialog - SecurityTerminalDialogue 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Page Intro Text :
"P2851374936" "Welcome to the facility operational computer system. Please enter your request below."
// Answer Text :
"P1732974048" "Gain access to the security center."
// Answer Text :
"P1691070887" "Activate facility self destruct sequence."
// Page AccessDenied Text :
"P2743627181" "Commander level security access code not recognized, please try again."
// Answer Text :
"P3160853433" "Find Commander Burns"
// Page BaseIsUnderAttack Text :
"P182647635" "Facility Self Destruct Sequence initializing...<br>Facility detonation should only occur in the following circumstances:<br>Imminent capture by enemy<br>Facility experiments have breached quarantine<br>All personnel dead or dying.<br> Please confirm that your intentions to destroy the facility match one or more of the criteria above."
// Answer Text :
"P1800541529" "Confirm: Begin self destruct sequence"
// Page SecurityProtocol Text :
"P3687284968" "Self Destruct Sequence has been confirmed. Council high command will be issued an automated alert of facility demolition. All data in the mainframe will receive remote back up and then be erased by a level 12 electro magnetic pulse.<br><br>Final confirmation of the above required."
// Answer Text :
"P931177619" "Final Confirmation: Blow it up!"
// Page DestroyBase Text :
"P4194858054" "Confirmed. Facility self destruct sequence initiated. This sequence cannot be revoked. This facility will be permanently deactivated."
// Answer Text :
"P1305222840" "Get out while the getting's good"

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Task Header Items 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// IntroString :
"P283045774" "Once you've taken out Jonas Howe, aka Nachtkrieg, you can convince the Council of your authenticy. Having infiltrated them you will have the opportunity to find and trigger the Council base's self destruct sequence, but it will need the base commander's code key. In the ensuing chaos you can escape, having destroyed a major Council base, but supplied the Council with 5th Column secrets."
// AcceptString :
"P2665163415" "Neutralize the defector Nachtkrieg and impersonate him"
// SendOffString :
"P3803358603" "The hostilities between the two groups will certainly flare up in the aftermath of your little ruse. But perhaps the two groups will finally consign themselves to killing each other off rather than beat around the bush about it."
// ActiveTaskString :
"P2064450910" "Infiltrate and Destroy the Council Base"
// YoureStillBusyString :
"P3064752953" "The only way you can get into that Council base is if you eliminate and impersonate the defector known as Nachtkrieg. You'd better hurry too, their meeting starts soon."
// TaskTitle :
"P3911804650" "<font face=title><scale 1.1><span align=center><color orange>Cherry Red Lipstick</color></span></scale></font><br><span align=center><color slategray><i>Villain Mission</i></color></span>"

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// MissionDef 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// EntryString :
"P3822547678" "The Council will be expecting a traitor. You'd better learn everything you can from the defector."
// ExitStringSuccess :
"P1057490799" "<font face=title><scale 1.1><span align=center><color orange>Cherry Red Lipstick</color></span></scale></font><br><span align=center><color slategray><i>Vigilante Mission</i></color></span><br><br>Not bad for a day's hard work. You managed to eliminate a notorious 5th Column operative, destroy a major Council facility, and rekindle the war between both groups. Sure, there might be some collateral damage when the conflict spills out into the streets, but in the bigger picture, what does that matter? The Council and 5th Column will be so focused on eliminating each other that they'll either succeed, or the heroes will finally swoop in and finish the job for them. And that is in the interest of everyone's greater good."
// Script Variable ChatMessage :
"P1629823733" "Nachtkrieg is down. Now question him... Extensively."
// Script Variable FloaterMessage :
"P1008643442" "Speak to Nachtkrieg"
// Script Variable ChatMessage :
"P3304808485" "You have claimed Nachtkrieg's identity. The Council will not attack you."
// Script Variable FloaterMessage :
"P931405209" "Nachtkrieg's identity assumed"
// Script Variable ChatMessage :
"P3803518963" "The Council base has assumed a high alert status. Your cover is blown, they will now attack you on sight!"
// Script Variable FloaterMessage :
"P663624568" "Identity compromised!"
// Script Variable ChatMessage :
"P682861589" "Facility self destruct sequence has been initiated. All personnel should evacuate immediately."
// Script Variable FloaterMessage :
"P3370056057" "Council base personnel are evacuating."
// Script Variable ObjectiveUIText :
"P411438217" "Speak to Commander Burns"
// Script Variable ObjectiveUIText :
"P1430770390" "Defeat Commander Burns"
// Script Variable BOSS_DISPLAYNAME :
"P1573678344" "Nachtkrieg"
// Script Variable BOSS_DISPLAYINFO :
"P3926341423" "Nachtkrieg is a 5th Column operative who has decided to defect to the Council with critical information."
// Script Variable BOSS_INACTIVE_DIALOG :
"P946695755" "I would have expected Commander Burns to have sent an escort..."
// Script Variable BOSS_ATTACK_DIALOG :
"P512604105" "{HeroName}? It's a trap!"
// Script Variable BOSS_1STBLOOD_DIALOG :
"P3707049945" "I have worked for years assembling this information. You will not stop me this close to completion!"
// Script Variable Greeting :
"P2913324463" "What is it you want, {HeroName}?"
// Script Variable SaysList :
"P3432514123" "This isn't over!"

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Objective - ScriptAgentHealth25 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Description :
"P2823661213" "Question and eliminate Nachtkrieg"
// Script Variable BOSS_DISPLAYNAME :
"P792895833" "Commander Burns"
// Script Variable BOSS_DISPLAYINFO :
"P428606717" "Commander Burns is the leader of this Council base and has been in contact with the double agent Nachtkrieg."
// Script Variable BOSS_75HEALTH_DIALOG :
"P1733473053" "I don't know what you were planning, {HeroName}, but if it was suicide, then your plan succeeded."
// Script Variable BOSS_25HEALTH_DIALOG :
"P1069124432" "This... Is not... How it was... Supposed to be!"
// Script Variable BOSS_DEAD_DIALOG :
"P2329560035" "Nooooooooo!"
// Script Variable Greeting :
"P3289437330" "Nachtkrieg, I assume? This moment has been a long time coming."
// Script Variable SaysList :
"P436930719" "This isn't Nachtkrieg! Stop {Hero.gender=male him|her}!"

