// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Task - AM_VigToVil_SL6-7_Task_05 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Dialog - BodyguardDialogueTree 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Page Intro Text :
"P2363872166" "I ain't helpin' you!"
// Answer Text :
"P927727436" "(Break her nose)"
// Page TortureMethod1 Text :
"P3437847790" "Ah! Mah nowse... You bwoke mah nowse!"
// Answer Text :
"P3154379503" "Cooperate, or I break something else."
// Page BodyguardTalks Text :
"P1240346980" "Awight, awight, I'll do whateva you want! What do you want?"
// Answer Text :
"P2818637154" "First, tell everyone that everything is fine."
// Answer Text :
"P2815091985" "Now, have that brother of yours meet us in the back."
// Answer Text :
"P3493500977" "I want this world to be rid of scum like you."
// Page BodyguardAlarmOff Text :
"P2533006785" "Awright, what do you want now?"
// Page BodyguardLovedOne Text :
"P4105018279" "Awright, there. Now what do you want?"
// Page BodyguardDies Text :
"P227907720" "What do you mean? Wait... No... NO!"
// Answer Text :
"P3470979208" ""Yes... It is the only way." (Kill Darling Dana)"
// Page BodyguardEnd Text :
"P144813804" "<color orange>Darling Dana falls limp to the floor, her life snuffed out by your hands, never to do evil ever again.</color>"
// Answer Text :
"P2722757549" "Now for your brother..."

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Dialog - LovedOneDialogueTree 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Page Intro Text :
"P161251911" "You monster! You killed my sister! What is wrong with you!?"
// Answer Text :
"P3462289719" "Call Annabella or she'll suffer the same fate."
// Page LovedOneTorture1 Text :
"P1566183403" "Annabella! Annabella! Help!"
// Answer Text :
"P2031610180" "Good boy. Now tell her I have you."
// Page LovedOneTorture2 Text :
"P3639622059" "Annabella! It's {HeroName}, {Hero.gender=male he|she}... {Hero.gender=male he|she} has me... {Hero.gender=male he|she} killed Dana... Please... Help me."
// Answer Text :
"P111943216" "Before you die, know this; Annabella will share your sister's fate!"
// Page LovedOneTorture3 Text :
"P692663527" "Anabella! No! It's a t..."
// Answer Text :
"P3898022631" ""Shhhh." (Kill Invincible Achilles)"
// Page LovedOneEnd Text :
"P2933463370" "<color orange>Invincible Achilles is not so invincible after all. You leave him in a heap on the ground and pick up the phone.</color>"
// Answer Text :
"P3638317113" "Face me, villain!"

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Dialog - BossDialogueTree 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Page Intro Text :
"P3835266896" "Why? Why!? We did everything they asked of us, everything they said we needed to do in order to pay for our crimes. Why have you done this?"
// Answer Text :
"P2635950526" "Everything, Annabella? Tell that to your victim's families..."
// Page BossText1 Text :
"P1404666004" "I wish I could. Every day I wish I could, but the court has forbidden me to make contact with them. What greater hell would you have me endure, {HeroName}? To what end?!"
// Answer Text :
"P4078072470" "Tell me what your plans really are!"
// Page BossText2 Text :
"P1140746330" "What evil plan? What are you talking about?! I'm telling you the truth, {HeroName}! All we wanted was to try and put behind us the evil of our past. If we could just bring some joy to the world, some good, maybe somehow we could find forgiveness..."
// Answer Text :
"P713191919" "The evil you've done and you expect me to buy this sob story?"
// Page BossText3 Text :
"P282129053" "I admit, I did some pretty wicked things in my time, but I've changed, we all did... All of us but you! We wanted nothing more than to try and atone for what we'd done, to bury the past behind us. But now you're the monster, {HeroName}! You're worse than I ever was! Why are you doing this? Why!?"
// Answer Text :
"P79030228" ""Because only in death can you truly be free of sin." (Kill Annabella)"
// Page MissionEnd Text :
"P1154330478" "<color orange>You leave Beautiful Annabella's mask on her face, more fitting of a funeral mask now. You have no desire to see the face of evil that lies beneath, because you know it wouldn't make any difference. Evil comes in every shape, size, and guise. This is a bitter lesson you have learned all too well.""
// Answer Text :
"P2650936206" "Find peace elsewhere, Annabella, there isn't enough to go around here."

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Task Header Items 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// IntroString :
"P4033984419" "Beautiful Annabella has always been able to work a crowd, and it seems she's at it again with her little trick. She's convinced the city that she's on the up and up and that her carnival attractions are just fun and games for the whole family. Luckily you know better. She did her time in the Zig, that's for sure, but when she got out she went right back to her Carnival brethren. Right back to her adoring minions and her loving strongman Invincible Achilles.<br><br>Scum like Annabell a never changes, and neither will the law that fails to deal with her kind of scum. It's up to you to reveal the wicked heart beating beneath her carefully crafted mask. She won't admit her plans, she's too strong for that, but if you were to harm her lover, there you may find a weakness you can exploit. Make Invincible Achilles scream, and Beautiful Annabella will cry tears of truth."
// AcceptString :
"P1855626971" "Teach Beautiful Annabella that all is fair in love and war"
// SendOffString :
"P3300033152" "You'll need to find Invincible Achilles in Annabella's posh little hideout. Make him suffer for all the evils Annabella has ever visited upon others. When she comes to his aid she will be faced with the same anguish she inflicted on so many others. Justice is seldom so poetic."
// ActiveTaskString :
"P1940756470" "Lure Beautiful Annabella into your trap."
// YoureStillBusyString :
"P4039523862" "Beautiful Annabella will be back at her hideout soon. You'll need to move quickly if you are to catch Invincible Achilles off guard and force Annabella into your trap. Once Achilles is screaming for mercy, Annabella won't be able to resist coming to his aid."
// TaskTitle :
"P2767211281" "<font face=title><scale 1.1><span align=center><color orange>A Tattered Flyer</color></span></scale></font><br><span align=center><color slategray><i>Vigilante Mission</i></color></span>"

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// MissionDef 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// EntryString :
"P1383587470" "Everyone in this place is guilty of innumerable crimes. That alone justifies the suffering you are about to deliver unto them."
// ExitStringSuccess :
"P1682658627" "<font face=title><scale 1.1><span align=center><color orange>VIGILANTE TO VILLAIN SL6-7 FIVE</color></span></scale></font><br><span align=center><color slategray><i>VIGILANTE MISSION</i></color></span><br><br>Your thoughts touch briefly on what Beautiful Annabella said to you before you gave her peace. You are nothing like her. She is the... was the lunatic. She was the one who perpetrated heinous crimes against the people. Did she really think that she could just sit in a cell and wash her hands of the justice she so richly deserved? Maybe she did, but you know right from wrong, justice from injustice. The will of the people has been enacted, vengeance has been served and Beautiful Annabella and her Carnival are no longer a threat to anyone, and that is all that really matters."
// Script Variable ObjectiveUIText :
"P216731373" "Interrogate Darling Dana"
// Script Variable ObjectiveUIText :
"P3920965699" "Find and capture Invincible Achilles"
// Script Variable ObjectiveUIText :
"P258715108" "Make Invincible Achilles scream for Annabella"
// Script Variable ObjectiveUIText :
"P3920010458" "Defeat Beautiful Annabella"
// Script Variable ObjectiveUIText :
"P1097324750" "Make Annabella talk"
// Script Variable ChatMessage :
"P3265747399" "Darling Dana slumps in defeat. Convince her to lure out Invincible Achilles"
// Script Variable FloaterMessage :
"P2842247894" "Speak to Darling Dana"
// Script Variable ChatMessage :
"P3938749945" "Invincible Achilles collapses, broken and beaten. Make him call out to Beautiful Annabella"
// Script Variable FloaterMessage :
"P3693741761" "Talk to Invincible Achilles"
// Script Variable ChatMessage :
"P3287728946" "Beautiful Annabella is finished, now learn her evil plan"
// Script Variable FloaterMessage :
"P1557749275" "Make Beautiful Annabella confess"
// Script Variable SaysList :
"P4205106234" "<t=5 caption x= 0.2 y=0.2 d=4><scale 1.75><color white><bgcolor FireBrick>Evewything's fwine, nobody panic. Fwalse alarm."
// Script Variable SaysList :
"P363603186" "<t=5 caption x= 0.2 y=0.4 d=4><scale 1.75><color white><bgcolor FireBrick>Achilles, I need to talk to you. Can you meet with me?"
// Script Variable SaysList :
"P1084482081" "<t=5 caption x= 0.2 y=0.2 d=4><scale 1.75><color white><bgcolor SteelBlue>Dana? Achilles? Oh... Oh no... What's happening! No!"
// Script Variable SaysList :
"P4282310130" "<t=5 caption x= 0.2 y=0.4 d=4><scale 1.75><color white><bgcolor SteelBlue>{HeroName}! Don't you dare hurt them! You'll never get away with this! Never!"
// Script Variable BOSS_DISPLAYNAME :
"P3890049224" "Darling Dana"
// Script Variable BOSS_DISPLAYINFO :
"P4099359690" "Darling Dana is Invincible Achilles's sister and one of Beautiful Annabella's closest friends. Together the three have performed a number of crime sprees across Paragon City. You suspect that this latest plot is no different."
// Script Variable BOSS_INACTIVE_DIALOG :
"P2668469713" "Will somebody please look into that alarm, it's ruining the vibe here. Ugh, fine, I'll look into it."
// Script Variable BOSS_ATTACK_DIALOG :
"P960816196" "{HeroName}? What brings you here... Hmph, can't let the past be the past, huh? It just irks you that we've gone goody-goody, huh?"
// Script Variable BOSS_75HEALTH_DIALOG :
"P3848308085" "Fine, you want to turn push into shove, then you got it!"
