"P3371181766" "Eleven"
// Script Variable BOSS_DISPLAYINFO :
"P3021763797" "Yes, he can go up 1 higher."
// Script Variable BOSS_INACTIVE_DIALOG :
"P1253828179" "Let's see what happens when I turn it up a notch!"
// Script Variable BOSS_ATTACK_DIALOG :
"P1531181038" "Welcome to the festivities!"
