// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Objective - ScriptSecondHeroBossRescued 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Objective - ScriptAmbushDefeated1 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Script Variable BOSS_DISPLAYNAME :
"P3198783301" "Baconator"
// Script Variable BOSS_DISPLAYINFO :
"P3419964273" "Most Freakshow adopt their advanced cybernetics so they can inflict greater and greater devastation upon the world. Baconator did so because his love of bacon was killing him. With virtually every internal organ replaced by plastic and steel he can enjoy his favorite food indefinitely. His ability to generate fifty thousand volts of electricity ensures that he is never without a way to cook it."
// Script Variable BOSS_INACTIVE_DIALOG :
"P2626611464" "<shout>Baaaaaaacon... Where are you bacon?"
// Script Variable BOSS_ATTACK_DIALOG :
"P3947946576" "<shout>There you are!"

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Objective - ScriptAmbushDefeated2 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Script Variable BOSS_DISPLAYNAME :
"P3815599523" "Juicy Juice"
// Script Variable BOSS_DISPLAYINFO :
"P4195215196" "Juicy Juice has got more juice than any other juicer. At least, that's his claim. Unfortunately nobody has been able to prove it, as Freakshow Juice-offs often result in power grid failures and out of control structure fires. The imminent arrival of peace officers just results in the whole thing getting called off in favor of a good scrap."
// Script Variable BOSS_INACTIVE_DIALOG :
"P3896920433" "<shout>I'm juiced up!"
// Script Variable BOSS_ATTACK_DIALOG :
"P701873075" "I'm gonna juice you like an orange, and by that I mean make your head explode!"

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Objective - ScriptAmbushDefeated3 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Script Variable BOSS_DISPLAYNAME :
"P2865981069" "Flatline"
// Script Variable BOSS_DISPLAYINFO :
"P4111484696" "Flatline got his moniker from kicking a massive power surge through a Paragon City hospital and flatlining thirty patients. All of them were saved by the quick actions of the medical staff, but when they aren't present, Flatline's ability to stop people's hearts is a deadly hobby."
// Script Variable BOSS_INACTIVE_DIALOG :
"P2116057782" "<shout>Sidewinder, baby, you're gonna give me a heart attack! Ah ha haha heh heh!"
// Script Variable BOSS_ATTACK_DIALOG :
"P2278301437" "Come on baby, can't you feel the sparks between us? Ah ha ha ha!"
// Script Variable BOSS_DISPLAYNAME :
"P3939841230" "Steel Mountain"
// Script Variable BOSS_DISPLAYINFO :
"P3991121285" "Steel Mountain is just like every other Tsoo boss. He has delusions of grandeur, a false sense of honor, and is all around just a backstabbing miscreant fated for an early grave."
// Script Variable BOSS_INACTIVE_DIALOG :
"P2735405673" "<shout>Those fools fell into my trap so easily. Everything is working perfectly."
// Script Variable BOSS_ATTACK_DIALOG :
"P2559276444" "Ahhhh, {HeroName}. I should have expected you to come here, and I see you brought Sidewinder with you. Good, together you will die!"
// Script Variable BOSS_75HEALTH_DIALOG :
"P1587274951" "It won't take long for me to convince more of you fools to come to your death in my trap."
// Script Variable BOSS_50HEALTH_DIALOG :
"P3434781048" "When word reaches the ears of other heroes that the Freakshow are responsible, they will come in droves to avenge you."
// Script Variable BOSS_25HEALTH_DIALOG :
"P686514982" "And it is I who will be there to lead them into battle, into my trap... Now die already!"

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Objective - ScriptVillainBossDefeated 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Description :
"P2247889733" "Defeat Steel Mountain"

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Reward - TaskSuccess 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Dialog :
"P2377875125" "You rescued Sidewinder, but it was not easy. Jim Matherson refused to believe that Steel Mountain was plotting his death, so in the end you killed him. At least in this way his death had meaning, for it was the leverage you needed to convince Sidewinder that Steel Mountain was going to betray them."

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Reward - ReturnSuccess 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// RandomFameString :
"P2577739227" "I heard the Freakshow killed Jim Matherson, but really it was a Tsoo double cross at the hands of that low life, Steel Mountain."

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Task - AM_VigToVil_SL6-7_Task_07 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Clue - ComputerSecurityAccess 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Clue Name :
"P1379570373" "Chief of Security's Cardkey"
// DetailString :
"P1165150946" "This cardkey can be used to access the Command/Control Network. You'll need to eliminate the access records though so this can't be pinned on you later."

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Dialog - SecurityTerminalDialogue 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Page Intro Text :
"P1439990535" "Welcome to Crey Biotech. Please insert your security cardkey now."
// Answer Text :
"P2270868364" "Look for information on the demonstration"
// Answer Text :
"P130586701" "Access the Command/Control Network"
// Page InformationPage1 Text :
"P604955802" "Today's demonstration is to be conducted by inventor Dr. Howard Gibson. It will feature and showcase the capabilities of the Super Chip developed in partnership with Dr. Howard Gibson with support from Crey Biotech.<br><br>The Super Chip not only provides the recipient with superior strength, reflexes, endurance, and cognitive reasoning, it also links them to the secure Command/Control Network. Through this network an organization will be able to monitor individuals equipped with Super Chips, share information between up to ten-thousand such individuals, administer remote medical aid, or, in the case of loss of cognitive function, issue commands to the individual to get them out of harms way, or complete the given task.<br><br>This secure demonstration will feature displays of increased reflexes, strength, endurance, pain tolerance, and some combat capabilities. In addition, the Command/Control Network will feature the remote command function, enabling the subject to carry out commands when rendered unconscious."
// Page AccessSubnetDenied Text :
"P1216169313" "I'm sorry, but you do not have the required security authorization. Please contact the on-duty Chief of Security to request clearance."
// Answer Text :
"P1768346653" "Find the Chief of Security"
// Page AccessSubnetPermitted Text :
"P3681931133" "Security subnet protocol accessed. Please insert command."
// Answer Text :
"P625187495" "Subject: Easton>Combat>Lethal>Maximum Force>Initialize"
// Page ConfirmOverride Text :
"P2148894510" "Command confirmed. Initializing subject for maximum force lethal combat.<br><br>Please insert command."
// Answer Text :
"P2747533535" "Network:Terminal 552>Security>Compromise>Self Termination"
// Page SelfDestruct Text :
"P1338192069" "<color orange>The terminal screen flickers and then the console suddenly explodes. Efficient.</color>"
// Answer Text :
"P2262932893" "Now to show Dr. Gibson and his guests the error of their ways"

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Task Header Items 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// IntroString :
"P2739910908" "Dr. Gibson's new Super Chip is designed to turn ordinary peace officers into super powered crime fighters. A quaint idea, but you know that in about 3 seconds flat someone like Nemesis will get his hands on it and turn it against us. You must ensure that never happens, and the only way to be certain is to make sure the technology is destroyed. All it will take is a small demonstration of the potential villainy that could be done with these chips, and the planned demonstration of the chip to a group of prospective investors will be the perfect opportunity."
// AcceptString :
"P1627755508" "Show the world that mass produced super powers are dangerous!"
// SendOffString :
"P1123346465" "If I can gain control of the subject through the network then I can have him attack the investors. Nobody in their right mind would support such a project with such an obvious flaw. Of course, then I need to disarm the situation and demonstrate how worthless the chips are by putting the test subject down. Dr. Gibson and his investors need to be reminded that what makes super powers super is the people wielding them. You can't mass produce power without also mass producing responsibility, and the world is already in dire need of the later without the addition of the former."
// ActiveTaskString :
"P585068886" "Take control of the super chip demonstration"
// YoureStillBusyString :
"P3282232546" "The facility is woefully undefended. It won't take you, or anyone else for that matter, very long to enter the facility and gain control of the command/control computer. This sort of carelessness is exactly why you need to stop the production of this chip and others like it. Such power cannot be allowed to be seized and used for evil."
// TaskTitle :
"P3247125651" "<font face=title><scale 1.1><span align=center><color orange>An Intelligence Leak</color></span></scale></font><br><span align=center><color slategray><i>Villain Mission</i></color></span>"

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// MissionDef 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// EntryString :
"P4099561109" "Dr. Gibson's voice comes over the intercom and echoes throughout the facility. The demonstration is beginning, you've timed this perfectly."
// ExitStringSuccess :
"P607956835" "<font face=title><scale 1.1><span align=center><color orange>An Intelligence Leak</color></span></scale></font><br><span align=center><color slategray><i>Vigilante Mission</i></color></span><br><br>You showed Dr. Gibson the error of his ways. The hubris of the unworthy was the direct cause of the injury and death of many innocents, as well as the unfortunate sacrifice of Sergeant Easton. Only you understand the responsibility of possessing powers so great . Only you can be trusted to defend the innocent from the deeds of the wicked."
// Script Variable ChatMessage :
"P980730924" "Sergeant Easton's Super Chip has turned off his pain receptors!"
// Script Variable FloaterMessage :
"P284371713" "Sergeant Easton is Recovering!"
// Script Variable ChatMessage :
"P3238663264" "Sergeant Easton's Super Chip is giving him an adrenaline surge!"
// Script Variable ObjectiveUIText :
"P642303867" "Override the command/control network security protocols"

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Objective - ScriptEnterMission 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Script Variable SaysList :
"P1178909383" "<t=5 caption x= 0.2 y=0.4 d=5><scale 1.75><color white><bgcolor SlateBlue>In conjunction with Crey Biotech, I, Dr. Howard Gibson, welcome you to today's demonstration of the new Super Chip!<t=10 caption x= 0.2 y=0.4 d=10><scale 1.75><color white><bgcolor SlateBlue>Sergeant Easton of Longbow has volunteered for today's demonstration. Everyone, le'ts give brave Mr. Easton a hand for volunteering to move Longbow and the Paragon Police force into the bleeding edge of law enforcement technology!<t=10 caption x= 0.2 y=0.4 d=10><scale 1.75><color white><bgcolor SlateBlue>And now for the boring specifics. Our Super Chip is installed onto Sergeant Easton's brain and linked remotely to a complex command control network. The network can supply the good sergeant with up to the nano-second information updates. Just one of these network computers can handle the operations and information demands of up to ten thousand officers."
// Script Variable SaysList :
"P616392309" "<t=10 caption x= 0.2 y=0.4 d=10><scale 1.75><color white><bgcolor SlateBlue>However, it is the Super Chip's ability to monitor and control a variety of small bio-tech implants throughout Sergeant Easton's body that makes it truly remarkable.<t=10 caption x= 0.2 y=0.4 d=10><scale 1.75><color white><bgcolor SlateBlue>With a single thought or input from the command/control network, Easton's body can be given super human levels of adrenaline, his pain receptors can be switched off, his heart can be restarted, and his memory can even be backed up and recorded on disk.<t=5 caption x= 0.2 y=0.4 d=5><scale 1.75><color white><bgcolor SlateBlue>He is, for all intents and purposes, a super human crime fighter."
// Script Variable SaysList :
"P4017457281" "<t=5 caption x= 0.2 y=0.4 d=5><scale 1.75><color white><bgcolor SlateBlue>Note that Sergeant Easton is incapable of managing to juggle even 2 tennis balls. Now, witness the change when the Super Chip is activated..."
// Script Variable SaysList :
"P480791663" "<t=7 caption x= 0.2 y=0.4 d=7><scale 1.75><color white><bgcolor SlateBlue>He can keep track of the three tennis balls easily. Let's try another three. Our lab tests have shown the ability to track and intercept, or dodge, over fifty moving targets, all at... wait... what's going on?<t=5 caption x= 0.2 y=0.4 d=4><scale 1.75><color white><bgcolor SlateBlue>Sergeant Easton, what's the matter? Wait! Cancel the demonstration!<t=5 caption x= 0.2 y=0.4 d=4><scale 1.75><color white><bgcolor SlateBlue>Everybody get out of here, now! Something has gone terribly wrong with his threat detection software. Seal him off in the demonstration room! Everybody get out!"
// Script Variable SaysList :
"P1532271922" "<t=10 caption x= 0.2 y=0.4 d=10><scale 1.75><color white><bgcolor SlateBlue>This is Dr. Gibson. Sergeant Easton, you are suffering a malfunction of your Super Chip threat processor. Please try to calm down and regain control. We will get you to a medical facility and get you assistance. Do you understand? We do not wish you any harm.<t=5 caption x= 0.2 y=0.4 d=5><scale 1.75><color white><bgcolor SlateBlue>Please, try to regain control. Think of your family, sergeant. Try to remember who you are, and what you are doing.<t=5 caption x= 0.2 y=0.2 d=4><scale 1.75><color white><bgcolor SlateBlue>{HeroName}? Have you come to help? We'd appreciate your assistance in apprehending Sergeant Easton. Be careful though, I'm not certain how extensive the malfunction is that caused this, he may use lethal force against you."
// Script Variable BOSS_DISPLAYNAME :
"P1038222854" "Chief of Security"
// Script Variable BOSS_INACTIVE_DIALOG :
"P2629318740" "<shout>Stay vigilant, we've got a report that a motion sensor was tripped in sector four. Could be a rat, but if it isn't it isn't anything we can't handle."
// Script Variable BOSS_ATTACK_DIALOG :
"P399815233" "Looks like we've got an intruder."

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Objective - ScriptSecurityBossDefeated 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Description :
"P3295885843" "Defeat the Chief of Security"

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Reward - Objective 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Dialog :
"P1049674316" "You've acquired the password you need to access and override the command/control network security protocols."
// Script Variable HOSTAGE_NAME :
"P1000628214" "Command/Control Network"
// Script Variable HOSTAGE_DISPLAY_INFO :
"P1893667009" "This computer terminal gives you direct access to the command/control network being used for today's demonstration."
// Script Variable CAPTOR_NAME :
"P333050393" "Patrol Guard"
// Script Variable Greeting :
"P1988582057" "Security Authorization Accepted."

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Objective - ScriptSecurityTerminalUsed 
