// Description :
"P2217071532" "Access the Command/Control Network"
// Script Variable BOSS_DISPLAYNAME :
"P2202290457" "Sergeant Easton"
// Script Variable BOSS_DISPLAYINFO :
"P3084366966" "Sergeant Easton is installed with a powerful new Super Chip. A technology developed for the greater good, but destined to be used for evil."
// Script Variable BOSS_INACTIVE_DIALOG :
"P3605729555" "M... Must... Neutralize all! No! Wh... What have I done!?"
// Script Variable BOSS_ATTACK_DIALOG :
"P2059271818" "{HeroName}!? No! Get away! I... I can't... control myself!"
// Script Variable BOSS_75HEALTH_DIALOG :
"P1365714503" "Can't... feel... pain..."
// Script Variable BOSS_25HEALTH_DIALOG :
"P4093934992" "Surge... of adrenaline... strength... returning!"
// Script Variable BOSS_DEAD_DIALOG :
"P3350840248" "F... forgive me..."
// Script Variable BOSS_KILLEDHERO_DIALOG :
"P2127398039" "C... can't... stop... somebody... help me!"
