// Objective - ScriptRobotBossDefeated 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Description :
"P1404584755" "Kill Sergeant Easton!"

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Reward - TaskSuccess 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Dialog :
"P238655769" "You've eliminated a dangerous and extremely foolish new technology as well as prevented it from ever falling into the hands of evil. At least, until the next brilliant scientist has delusions of doing the right thing."

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Reward - ReturnSuccess 
