"P365685960" "You read the words of power on the Altar of Darkness and the ritual of pain begins!"

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Reward - TaskSuccess 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Dialog :
"P537699228" "Though you tried to convince Sarah Winters that her methods would never stop the Circle, she doubted the truth of your words and tried to stop you from delivering the only form of justice that the Circle understands; death. You tried to show her what her flawed sense of right and wrong would get her, but in the end she attacked you, falsely concluding that your methods were evil. In the end, her lack of conviction proved that she was too weak to defeat you, let alone her real enemies."

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Reward - ReturnSuccess 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// RandomFameString :
"P2902620398" "I heard that Sarah Winters died trying to stop a great evil from coming into this world. She was such a role model."
